txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Muted dust from the Dead in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'They will not rise again to threaten any in this world.'
'The Dead rise and walk to the east and along the Kingsway. There are two types of residue left behind when they fall, and we want them both to see that they rise no more.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Muted Dust
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of muted dust.
Deliver the muted dust to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting muted dust from the Dead surrounding Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Muted dust from the Dead in the lands surrounding the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
